### Web & API (5개)

#### 14. **cookie-c** - Cookie Handling
```c
#include "kcookie.h"

// 쿠키 생성
cookie_t *cookie = cookie_create("session", "abc123");
cookie_set_path(cookie, "/");
cookie_set_domain(cookie, "example.com");
cookie_set_max_age(cookie, 3600); // 1시간

// 쿠키 파싱
cookie_t *parsed = cookie_parse("session=abc123; Path=/; Domain=example.com");

// 쿠키 직렬화
char *str = cookie_serialize(cookie);
```

#### 15. **cookie-parser-c** - Cookie Parsing Middleware
```c
#include "kcookie_parser.h"

