## 🔧 사용 예제

### UUID 생성
```c
#include "uuid-c/include/kuuid.h"
#include <stdio.h>

int main() {
    uuid_t id = uuid_v4_generate();
    char str[37];
    uuid_to_string(id, str);
    printf("Generated UUID: %s\n", str);
    return 0;
}
```

컴파일:
```bash
gcc -I uuid-c/include example.c uuid-c/src/kuuid.c -o example
./example
```

### HTTP 서버
```c
#include "express-c/include/kexpress.h"

void hello_handler(request_t *req, response_t *res) {
    response_send(res, "Hello World!");
}

int main() {
    server_t *server = express_create();
    express_get(server, "/", hello_handler);
    express_listen(server, 3000);
    return 0;
}
```

컴파일 & 실행:
```bash
gcc -I express-c/include example.c express-c/src/kexpress.c -o server
./server
# 브라우저: http://localhost:3000
```

